scripts.script:
(do
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (. shape :renderDefault canvas)
  (. canvas :strokeRect
        (. shape :left)
        (. shape :top)
        (. shape :right)
        (. shape :bottom) seed))

(do
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (. shape :renderDefault canvas)
  (. canvas :line
    (. shape :left)
    (. shape :top)
    (. shape :right)
    (. shape :top) seed))

(do
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (. shape :renderDefault canvas)
  (. canvas :line
    (. shape :left)
    (. shape :top)
    (. shape :right)
    (. shape :top) seed))

children.name: Class
children.description: You can suppress template, attribute and operation compartments by extended properties

scripts.script:
(do
  (def! l (+ (. shape :left) 15))
  (def! r (. shape :right))
  (def! t (. shape :top))
  (def! b (. shape :bottom))
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (. canvas :fillRect l t r b seed)
  (. canvas :rect (- l 15) (+ t 10) (+ l 15) (+ t 25) seed)
  (. canvas :rect (- l 15) (+ t 35) (+ l 15) (+ t 50) seed)
  (. canvas :polyline [[l (+ t 10)] [l t] [r t] [r b] [l b] [l (+ t 50)]] seed)
  (. canvas :line l (+ t 25) l (+ t 35) seed))

children.name: Interface (Socket)
children.description: You can change orientation and it can contains an interface ball.

scripts.script:
(do
  (def! c (. shape :getCenter))
  (def! w (. shape :width))
  (def! o (. shape :getPropertyValue "Orientation"))
  (def! x (nth c 0))
  (def! y (nth c 1))
  (def! r (/ w 2))
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (if (= o "up") (. canvas :arc x y r 0 180 seed))
  (if (= o "down") (. canvas :arc x y r 180 360 seed))
  (if (= o "left") (. canvas :arc x y r -90 90 seed))
  (if (= o "right") (. canvas :arc x y r 90 270 seed)))

children.name: Select
children.description: Use "open" property for show and hide options

scripts.script:
(do
  (def! g 8)
  (def! l (. shape :left))
  (def! r (. shape :right))
  (def! t (. shape :top))
  (def! b (. shape :bottom))
  (def! h (. shape :height))
  (def! xc (- r (/ h 2)))
  (def! yc (+ t (* h 0.65)))
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (. shape :renderDefault canvas)
  (. canvas :line (- r h) t (- r h) b seed)
  (. canvas :polyline [[(- xc g) (- yc g)] [xc yc] [(+ xc g) (- yc g)]] seed))

(do
  (def! m 4)
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (. shape :renderDefault canvas)
  (if (. shape :getPropertyValue "Checked")
    (do
      (. canvas :setFillColor (. shape :strokeColor))
      (. canvas :ellipse
         (+ (. shape :left) m)
         (+ (. shape :top) m)
         (- (. shape :right) m)
         (- (. shape :bottom) m) seed))))

(do
  (def! checked (. shape :getPropertyValue "Checked"))
  (def! h (. shape :height))
  (def! l (if checked (- (. shape :right) h) (. shape :left)))
  (def! r (. shape :right))
  (def! t (. shape :top))
  (def! b (. shape :bottom))
  (def! m 2)
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (if checked (. canvas :setFillColor (. shape :strokeColor)))
  (. shape :renderDefault canvas)
  (. canvas :setFillColor (. shape :fillColor))
  (. canvas :ellipse (+ l m) (+ t m) (+ l (- h m)) (- b m) seed))

(do
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (. shape :renderDefault canvas)
  (. canvas :line
    (. shape :left)
    (. shape :top)
    (. shape :left)
    (. shape :bottom) seed))

(do
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (. shape :renderDefault canvas)
  (. canvas :line
    (. shape :left)
    (. shape :top)
    (. shape :left)
    (. shape :bottom) seed))

(do
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (. canvas :line
    (. shape :left)
    (. shape :top)
    (. shape :right)
    (. shape :top) seed))

(do
  (def! l (. shape :left))
  (def! r (. shape :right))
  (def! t (. shape :top))
  (def! b (. shape :bottom))
  (def! w (. shape :width))
  (def! wh (/ w 2))
  (def! g (/ (. shape :height) 8))
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (. canvas :path
     [[:M l (+ t g)]
      [:A wh g 0 0 1 r (+ t g)]
      [:L r (- b g)]
      [:A wh g 0 0 1 l (- b g)]
      [:Z]] seed)
  (. canvas :strokePath [[:M l (+ t g)] [:A wh g 0 0 0 r (+ t g)]] seed)
  (. shape :renderText canvas))

(do
  (def! l (. shape :left))
  (def! r (. shape :right))
  (def! t (. shape :top))
  (def! b (. shape :bottom))
  (def! g 10)
  (def! wg (/ (- (. shape :width) 10) 2))
  (def! cr (* g 8))
  (def! m 6)
  (def! m2 (* m 2))
  (def! seed (. shape :getSeed))
  (. canvas :path
     [[:M l t]
      [:L (- r m2) t]
      [:L (- r m2) (+ t m)]
      [:L (- r m) (+ t m)]
      [:L (- r m) (+ t m2)]
      [:L r (+ t m2)]
      [:L r (- b g)]
      [:A cr cr 0 0 0 (- r wg) (- b g)]
      [:A cr cr 0 0 1 (+ l m2) (- b g)]
      [:L (+ l m2) (- b (+ g m))]
      [:L (+ l m) (- b (+ g m))]
      [:L (+ l m) (- b (+ g m2))]
      [:L l (- b (+ g m2))]
      [:Z]] seed)
  (. canvas :polyline [[(- r m) (+ t m2)] [(+ l m2) (+ t m2)] [(+ l m2) (- b (+ g m))]] seed)
  (. canvas :polyline [[(- r m) (+ t m)] [(+ l m) (+ t m)] [(+ l m) (- b (+ g m))]] seed)
  (. shape :renderText canvas))
